{
  "stem": "9538.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you were sent to the right, you could go back into your-- into your barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you were sent left, you were taken away straight outside to wait in columns, to wait outside the gates.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We came back that evening fairly late.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as I went through this selection, I went into the barracks, went to my mother's bed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can't call it bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were five beds on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was right on the fifth, being young and athletic, and my mother was at the bottom.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother's bed was not touched, so that means she wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked-- she worked for the [GERMAN] barracks, infantry barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where her workshop was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I had come back already, 4 o'clock in the afternoon, so I knew that she was on the other side-- that she was selected for the other side.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I can see it-- to the side to die and not to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If she were to live, she would have been in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I crawled down a fire escape, which was outside this barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the whole yard was surrounded by SS with rifle butts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I still hear until now, where does-- where does the old goat think she is going?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he pulled me down from the fire escape ladder and hit me with his rifle butt over my head and my back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I've got a nasty injury on my back, which makes me a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gives me a lot of trouble, especially now I've got arthritis in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm sometimes in agony.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've still got some traces of-- the yard had, sort of, gravel.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
